title: "Hogbook" (w/ Maria Bamford)
itunes:title: "Hogbook" (w/ Maria Bamford)
description:
Yex of courx you’re going to LOVE this ep!! 

The legendary, inspirational, fantastique Maria Bamford is in-studio and we are oh so happy. I hope you’ve physically, emotionally, and spiritually prepared yourself because this episode covers a lot of cultural ground in 1 hr 13 mins: Working at Disney, music videos that are getting cooler and cooler (because of the money), the impact of Maroon 5’s “Girls Like You” music video, Unicorns in saunas, Pug ranches, raccoons with IBS, Three’s Company, Pepé Le Pew, luxury (in general), and of course, HOGBOOK!
